The '''Kinkees''' were a faction that fought during the [[Aerial Plankton Uprising]]. The combined efforts of [[Ebenn Q3 Baobab/Legends|Ebenn Q3 Baobab]] and [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Gordun]] resulted in their defeat.

